      'Assists other departments when necessary',
      'Maintain a safe, organized, and clean work environment to ensure safety',
      'Assist in creating and following QC processes',
      'Work some weekend and after-hours as needed',
      'Comply with company policies and procedures',
      'Perform additional duties as assigned',
    ],
